        "description": "<p>Example Usage</p>\n<pre><code>$cmb-&gt;add_field( array(\n    'name' =&gt; 'Markdown Enabled Field',\n    'type' =&gt; 'text_markdown',\n    'id'   =&gt; 'test_markdown',\n    'sanitization_cb' =&gt; 'markdown_sanitize'\n) );\n</code></pre>\n<p>It works with repeatable fields as well!</p>\n",
